it.polito.dp2.NFFG

Interface TraversalPolicyReader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    NamedEntityReader, PolicyReader, ReachabilityPolicyReader

    public interface TraversalPolicyReader
extends ReachabilityPolicyReader
    An interface for accessing the data associated to a Traversal policy, which is a particular kind of Reachability policy. A Traversal policy specifies a property that is the existence of a path in the NF-FG that connects a source node to a destination node, and the fact that all such paths traverse a set of network functionalities (e.g., firewall, NAT, DPI,etc.).
